N. J. COIN et al. v. UNITED STATES of America. No. 4713. Circuit Court of Appeals, Seventh Circuit. April 9, 1935.

Before EVANS, SPARKS, and ALSCHULER, Circuit Judges.

PER CURIAM.

Upon the filing of a consent to dismissal of this appeal by counsel for appellants, it is now here ordered and adjudged by this court that this appeal be, and the same is hereby, dismissed.
